#: templates/website/about.html:5 templates/website/about.html:16
#: templates/website/about.html:24
msgid "À propos de Revival | Vision, mission et impact digital en Afrique"
msgstr "About Revival | Vision, mission and digital impact in Africa"

#: templates/website/about.html:8
msgid ""
"Revival transforme les idées en solutions digitales puissantes pour aider "
"les entrepreneurs et les entreprises à lancer, structurer et développer "
"leurs activités en Afrique."
msgstr ""
"Revival transforms ideas into powerful digital solutions to help "
"entrepreneurs and businesses launch, structure and grow their businesses in "
"Africa."

#: templates/website/about.html:9
msgid ""
"à propos Revival, entreprise technologique RDC, transformation digitale "
"Afrique, solutions digitales Kinshasa, innovation entrepreneuriale Afrique"
msgstr ""
"about Revival, technology company DRC, digital transformation Africa, "
"digital solutions Kinshasa, entrepreneurial innovation Africa"

#: templates/website/about.html:17
msgid ""
"Revival met la technologie au service de l'Afrique pour transformer les "
"idées en solutions digitales concrètes, performantes et utiles."
msgstr ""
"Revival puts technology at the service of Africa to transform ideas into "
"concrete, efficient and useful digital solutions."

#: templates/website/about.html:25
msgid ""
"Nous aidons les entrepreneurs et les entreprises à transformer leurs "
"ambitions en solutions digitales puissantes."
msgstr ""
"We help entrepreneurs and businesses transform their ambitions into powerful"
" digital solutions."

#: templates/website/about.html:32
msgid "À propos de Revival"
msgstr "About Revival"

#: templates/website/about.html:34
msgid ""
"Revival est une entreprise technologique qui transforme les idées en "
"solutions digitales puissantes pour créer des opportunités en Afrique."
msgstr ""
"Revival is a technology company that transforms ideas into powerful digital "
"solutions to create opportunities in Africa."

#: templates/website/about.html:37 templates/website/coming-soon.html:325
#: templates/website/coming-soon.html:337
msgid "Revival"
msgstr "Revival"

#: templates/website/about.html:390
msgid "À propos de nous"
msgstr "About Us"

#: templates/website/about.html:391
msgid "Transformer les idées en"
msgstr "Transform ideas into"

#: templates/website/about.html:391
msgid "solutions digitales puissantes"
msgstr "powerful digital solutions"

#: templates/website/about.html:392
msgid ""
"Revival est bien plus qu’une entreprise technologique. C’est une vision, un "
"mouvement et une mission : mettre le digital au service de l’Afrique, et en "
"particulier de la République Démocratique du Congo, pour aider les "
"entrepreneurs, les entreprises et les porteurs de projets à construire, "
"structurer et faire grandir leurs activités."
msgstr ""
"Revival is much more than a technology company. It is a vision, a movement "
"and a mission: to put digital at the service of Africa, and in particular "
"the Democratic Republic of Congo, to help entrepreneurs, businesses and "
"project leaders to build, structure and grow their activities."

#: templates/website/about.html:394
msgid "Parler à notre équipe"
msgstr "Talk to our team"

#: templates/website/about.html:395 templates/website/home.html:104
msgid "Voir nos réalisations"
msgstr "See our achievements"

#: templates/website/about.html:400
msgid "Notre conviction"
msgstr "Our belief"

#: templates/website/about.html:401
msgid ""
"Une idée, même simple, peut devenir un projet à fort impact lorsqu’elle est "
"bien accompagnée, bien structurée et bien exécutée."
msgstr ""
"An idea, even a simple one, can become a high-impact project when it is well"
" supported, well structured and well executed."

#: templates/website/about.html:403
msgid "Créer des solutions concrètes, utiles et performantes."
msgstr "Create concrete, useful and effective solutions."

#: templates/website/about.html:404
msgid "Accompagner les ambitions avec une vraie lecture du marché africain."
msgstr "Support ambitions with a real reading of the African market."

#: templates/website/about.html:405
msgid "Transformer la technologie en levier de croissance durable."
msgstr "Transform technology into a lever for sustainable growth."

#: templates/website/about.html:415
msgid "Notre mission"
msgstr "Our mission"

#: templates/website/about.html:416
msgid "Créer des opportunités réelles grâce au digital"
msgstr "Create real opportunities thanks to digital"

#: templates/website/about.html:417
msgid ""
"Dans un contexte où le numérique redéfinit profondément les règles du jeu, "
"Revival a fait un choix clair : utiliser la technologie comme un outil de "
"structuration, de performance et d’accélération pour les acteurs économiques"
" africains."
msgstr ""
"In a context where digital technology is profoundly redefining the rules of "
"the game, Revival has made a clear choice: to use technology as a tool for "
"structuring, performance and acceleration for African economic players."

#: templates/website/about.html:418
msgid ""
"Nous aidons les entrepreneurs et les entreprises à transformer leurs "
"ambitions en solutions concrètes, performantes et viables. Notre rôle n’est "
"pas seulement de développer des outils. Notre rôle est de rendre les projets"
" plus clairs, plus solides et plus capables de grandir."
msgstr ""
"We help entrepreneurs and businesses transform their ambitions into "
"concrete, efficient and viable solutions. Our role is not just to develop "
"tools. Our role is to make projects clearer, stronger and more capable of "
"growing."

#: templates/website/about.html:419
msgid ""
"À travers chaque plateforme, chaque application et chaque système que nous "
"concevons, nous cherchons à créer de la valeur utile, durable et exploitable"
" sur le terrain."
msgstr ""
"Through every platform, every application and every system we design, we "
"seek to create useful, sustainable and actionable value in the field."

#: templates/website/about.html:425
msgid "Notre positionnement"
msgstr "Our positioning"

#: templates/website/about.html:426
msgid ""
"Nous ne concevons pas la technologie comme une fin. Nous la concevons comme "
"un levier de réussite."
msgstr "We do not see technology as an end. We see it as a lever for success."

#: templates/website/about.html:427
msgid ""
"Revival accompagne chaque projet avec exigence, sens stratégique et "
"compréhension des réalités locales. C’est cette combinaison entre vision "
"business, exécution digitale et lecture du marché africain qui donne à notre"
" approche sa force."
msgstr ""
"Revival supports each project with rigor, strategic sense and understanding "
"of local realities. It is this combination of business vision, digital "
"execution and reading of the African market that gives our approach its "
"strength."

#: templates/website/about.html:436
msgid "Ce qui nous définit"
msgstr "What defines us"

#: templates/website/about.html:437
msgid "Une approche claire, engagée et orientée impact"
msgstr "A clear, committed and impact-oriented approach"

#: templates/website/about.html:445
msgid "Vision"
msgstr "Vision"

#: templates/website/about.html:446
msgid ""
"Faire du digital un moteur d’opportunités, d’organisation et de croissance "
"pour les entrepreneurs et les entreprises qui veulent construire "
"sérieusement."
msgstr ""
"Making digital a driver of opportunities, organization and growth for "
"entrepreneurs and companies who want to build seriously."

#: templates/website/about.html:453
msgid "Innovation utile"
msgstr "Useful innovation"

#: templates/website/about.html:454
msgid ""
"Nous privilégions les solutions qui résolvent de vrais problèmes, améliorent"
" l’efficacité et donnent aux projets une base plus solide pour évoluer."
msgstr ""
"We prioritize solutions that solve real problems, improve efficiency, and "
"give projects a stronger foundation to scale."

#: templates/website/about.html:461
msgid "Valeur réelle"
msgstr "Actual value"

#: templates/website/about.html:462
msgid ""
"Notre ambition est de produire des solutions capables d’aider à lancer, "
"gérer, vendre, structurer ou automatiser avec plus de maîtrise et plus "
"d’impact."
msgstr ""
"Our ambition is to produce solutions capable of helping to launch, manage, "
"sell, structure or automate with greater control and greater impact."

#: templates/website/about.html:472
msgid "Revival conçoit un écosystème, pas seulement des interfaces."
msgstr "Revival designs an ecosystem, not just interfaces."

#: templates/website/about.html:473
msgid ""
"Chaque projet est pensé comme un outil de croissance, d’organisation et "
"d’exécution plus intelligente."
msgstr ""
"Each project is designed as a tool for growth, organization and smarter "
"execution."

#: templates/website/about.html:479
msgid "Ce que nous construisons"
msgstr "What we build"

#: templates/website/about.html:480
msgid "Des solutions pensées pour lancer, gérer et faire grandir"
msgstr "Solutions designed to launch, manage and grow"

#: templates/website/about.html:481
msgid ""
"Nous concevons des applications mobiles, des plateformes digitales, des "
"systèmes de gestion intelligents et des solutions automatisées qui "
"permettent aux entreprises de gagner en efficacité, de mieux servir leurs "
"clients et de se développer plus rapidement."
msgstr ""
"We design mobile applications, digital platforms, intelligent management "
"systems and automated solutions that enable businesses to become more "
"efficient, serve their customers better and grow faster."

#: templates/website/about.html:482
msgid ""
"Notre travail consiste à rendre les projets plus lisibles, plus performants "
"et plus capables de passer à l’échelle. Cela demande à la fois de la "
"technique, de la structure et une vraie compréhension du contexte dans "
"lequel les solutions seront utilisées."
msgstr ""
"Our work consists of making projects more readable, more efficient and more "
"capable of scaling up. This requires both technique, structure and a real "
"understanding of the context in which the solutions will be used."

#: templates/website/about.html:486
msgid "Applications et plateformes digitales"
