#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:103
msgid ""
"Fournir des solutions professionnelles, performantes et adaptées aux "
"réalités du marché africain."
msgstr ""
"Provide professional, efficient solutions adapted to the realities of the "
"African market."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:104
msgid ""
"Assurer un accompagnement technique et stratégique aligné sur les objectifs "
"du partenariat."
msgstr ""
"Provide technical and strategic support aligned with the objectives of the "
"partnership."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:105
msgid "Protéger la confidentialité des informations échangées."
msgstr "Protect the confidentiality of information exchanged."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:106
msgid ""
"Respecter les termes convenus dans les accords spécifiques conclus avec le "
"partenaire."
msgstr ""
"Respect the terms agreed in the specific agreements concluded with the "
"partner."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:107
msgid ""
"Mettre à disposition, lorsque cela est prévu, les outils, supports ou "
"ressources utiles à la collaboration."
msgstr ""
"Make available, when planned, tools, supports or resources useful for "
"collaboration."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:114
msgid ""
"Respecter les valeurs, l’image, les standards de qualité et les intérêts "
"légitimes de Revival."
msgstr ""
"Respect the values, image, quality standards and legitimate interests of "
"Revival."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:115
msgid ""
"Fournir des informations exactes, à jour et exploitables pour la bonne "
"conduite du partenariat."
msgstr ""
"Provide accurate, up-to-date and usable information for the proper conduct "
"of the partnership."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:116
msgid "Collaborer avec professionnalisme, transparence et bonne foi."
msgstr "Collaborate with professionalism, transparency and good faith."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:117
msgid ""
"S’abstenir de tout comportement susceptible de porter atteinte à Revival, à "
"ses clients ou à ses activités."
msgstr ""
"Refrain from any behavior likely to harm Revival, its customers or its "
"activities."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:118
msgid ""
"Honorer les obligations contractuelles, financières ou opérationnelles qui "
"lui incombent."
msgstr "Honor its contractual, financial or operational obligations."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:124
msgid ""
"Revival peut proposer différents formats de collaboration, chacun pouvant "
"donner lieu à des conditions particulières."
msgstr ""
"Revival can offer different collaboration formats, each of which may give "
"rise to specific conditions."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:126
msgid ""
"Partenariat commercial : le partenaire intervient comme apporteur "
"d’affaires, distributeur ou revendeur et peut percevoir une commission selon"
" les ventes réalisées."
msgstr ""
"Commercial partnership: the partner acts as a business provider, distributor"
" or reseller and can receive a commission based on sales made."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:127
msgid ""
"Partenariat stratégique : collaboration de moyen ou long terme autour de "
"projets communs, d’un marché, d’un produit ou d’un écosystème partagé."
msgstr ""
"Strategic partnership: medium or long-term collaboration around common "
"projects, a market, a product or a shared ecosystem."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:128
msgid ""
"Partenariat technologique : intégration de solutions, co-développement, "
"interconnexion technique ou contribution d’expertise."
msgstr ""
"Technological partnership: integration of solutions, co-development, "
"technical interconnection or contribution of expertise."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:129
msgid ""
"Partenariat institutionnel : coopération avec des organisations, "
"entreprises, institutions publiques ou privées."
msgstr ""
"Institutional partnership: cooperation with organizations, companies, public"
" or private institutions."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:131
msgid ""
"Chaque modèle peut être complété par un accord spécifique détaillant les "
"obligations opérationnelles, commerciales ou financières propres à la "
"collaboration concernée."
msgstr ""
"Each model can be supplemented by a specific agreement detailing the "
"operational, commercial or financial obligations specific to the "
"collaboration concerned."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:135
msgid "6. Rémunération et commissions"
msgstr "6. Remuneration and commissions"

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:136
msgid ""
"Les modalités de rémunération dépendent de la nature du partenariat et sont "
"définies dans les accords applicables."
msgstr ""
"Remuneration arrangements depend on the nature of the partnership and are "
"defined in the applicable agreements."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:138
msgid "Commissions sur ventes ou sur projets apportés."
msgstr "Commissions on sales or projects contributed."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:139
msgid "Partage de revenus ou répartition contractuelle des gains."
msgstr "Revenue sharing or contractual distribution of earnings."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:140
msgid "Honoraires fixes ou forfaits de prestation."
msgstr "Fixed fees or service packages."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:141
msgid "Bonus de performance, selon les objectifs convenus."
msgstr "Performance bonus, according to agreed objectives."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:143
msgid ""
"Les paiements sont effectués selon les délais, justificatifs et conditions "
"prévus dans l’accord spécifique conclu entre les parties."
msgstr ""
"Payments are made according to the deadlines, supporting documents and "
"conditions provided for in the specific agreement concluded between the "
"parties."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:148
msgid ""
"Toutes les informations techniques, stratégiques, commerciales, financières "
"ou opérationnelles échangées dans le cadre du partenariat sont "
"confidentielles, sauf mention contraire écrite."
msgstr ""
"All technical, strategic, commercial, financial or operational information "
"exchanged within the framework of the partnership is confidential, unless "
"otherwise stated in writing."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:149
msgid ""
"Le Partenaire s’engage à ne pas divulguer, reproduire, exploiter ou "
"transmettre ces informations à un tiers sans autorisation écrite préalable "
"de Revival."
msgstr ""
"The Partner undertakes not to disclose, reproduce, exploit or transmit this "
"information to a third party without prior written authorization from "
"Revival."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:154
msgid ""
"Sauf disposition contraire convenue par écrit, les solutions, technologies, "
"marques, méthodologies, contenus, visuels, documents et éléments créés ou "
"exploités par Revival demeurent sa propriété exclusive."
msgstr ""
"Unless otherwise agreed in writing, the solutions, technologies, brands, "
"methodologies, content, visuals, documents and elements created or exploited"
" by Revival remain its exclusive property."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:155
msgid ""
"Le Partenaire ne peut utiliser les éléments appartenant à Revival que dans "
"le cadre strict du partenariat et selon les autorisations accordées."
msgstr ""
"The Partner may only use elements belonging to Revival within the strict "
"framework of the partnership and according to the authorizations granted."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:160
msgid ""
"Le partenariat peut être conclu pour une durée déterminée ou indéterminée, "
"selon les termes fixés entre les parties."
msgstr ""
"The partnership can be concluded for a fixed or indefinite period, depending"
" on the terms agreed between the parties."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:162
msgid ""
"Chaque partie peut y mettre fin en cas de non-respect des engagements "
"convenus."
msgstr ""
"Either party may terminate it in the event of non-compliance with the agreed"
" commitments."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:163
msgid ""
"Une résiliation peut également intervenir en cas de comportement "
"préjudiciable, de force majeure ou de motif légitime prévu par l’accord "
"applicable."
msgstr ""
"Termination may also occur in the event of harmful behavior, force majeure "
"or legitimate reason provided for in the applicable agreement."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:164
msgid ""
"Sauf faute grave ou urgence particulière, une notification préalable doit "
"être adressée à l’autre partie."
msgstr ""
"Except in the event of serious misconduct or a particular emergency, prior "
"notification must be sent to the other party."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:170
msgid ""
"Chaque partie demeure responsable de ses actes, déclarations, engagements et"
" obligations dans le cadre du partenariat."
msgstr ""
"Each party remains responsible for its actions, declarations, commitments "
"and obligations within the framework of the partnership."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:171
msgid ""
"Revival ne saurait être tenu responsable des dommages, pertes ou "
"conséquences résultant d’une mauvaise utilisation de ses services, d’une "
"information erronée fournie par le partenaire ou d’un manquement imputable à"
" ce dernier."
msgstr ""
"Revival cannot be held responsible for damage, losses or consequences "
"resulting from improper use of its services, from incorrect information "
"provided by the partner or from a breach attributable to the latter."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:176
msgid ""
"Le Partenaire s’engage à respecter les lois, règlements et obligations "
"applicables à son activité, notamment en matière de commerce, fiscalité, "
"concurrence, propriété intellectuelle et protection des données."
msgstr ""
"The Partner undertakes to respect the laws, regulations and obligations "
"applicable to its activity, in particular with regard to trade, taxation, "
"competition, intellectual property and data protection."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:181
msgid ""
"Revival se réserve le droit de mettre à jour les présentes conditions afin "
"de tenir compte de l’évolution de ses activités, de ses offres ou du cadre "
"réglementaire applicable."
msgstr ""
"Revival reserves the right to update these conditions in order to take into "
"account developments in its activities, its offers or the applicable "
"regulatory framework."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:182
msgid ""
"Les partenaires seront informés de toute modification importante par les "
"canaux appropriés."
msgstr ""
"Partners will be informed of any significant changes through the appropriate"
" channels."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:186
msgid "13. Droit applicable et juridiction"
msgstr "13. Applicable law and jurisdiction"

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:187
msgid ""
"Les présentes conditions sont régies par les lois applicables en République "
"Démocratique du Congo et, le cas échéant, par les principes pertinents du "
"droit OHADA lorsque ceux-ci trouvent à s’appliquer."
msgstr ""
"These conditions are governed by the laws applicable in the Democratic "
"Republic of Congo and, where applicable, by the relevant principles of OHADA"
" law where these apply."

#: templates/website/conditions-partenariat.html:188
msgid ""
"Tout litige relatif à leur interprétation, exécution ou validité relève des "
"juridictions compétentes, sauf mécanisme particulier prévu dans un accord "
"spécifique conclu entre les parties."
msgstr ""
"Any dispute relating to their interpretation, execution or validity falls "
"under the competent jurisdictions, unless there is a specific mechanism "
"provided for in a specific agreement concluded between the parties."

